Hi friends, Here I have created a program of Encrypting text using Vignere cipher in JAVA. I have used very simple and straightforward approach. 
My program include both methods i.e. Encryption and Decryption. I hope you will enjoy it. Happy Coding :)

*******Output*******

Enter your text:
My favourite animal is Dog.
Enter your key:
encryption
*****Menu****
1. Encryption
2. Decryption
Enter your choice: 
1
Your Encrypted Text is:
Ql hrtdnzwgi npzkpe qg Qst.
